title: Goals as a Developer
content: To consistently write quality code that follows industry best practices
To make a noticeably positive impact on a team, product or company
To constantly improve and learn using all available resources

title: Ideal Work Environment
content: Has compassionate team members who enjoy collaborating
Creates a productive atmosphere to maximize efficiency
Possesses an overall positive and optimistic ambience

title: Interests & Hobbies
content: DJing and creating fun beats in Ableton Live
Casual and competitive gaming with friends
